{
  "stem": "27390.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One was not very far from us and it had a big dome.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You could see it from miles away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it had a-- there was a, a cantor and a choir.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was beautiful inside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The, the, the, the decor-- decor-- decorations inside, the-- it was very elaborate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in the morning, we didn't go to that synagogue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We went to a small shtieble.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A shtieble is where usually there is a rabbi who is a descendent of a famous rabbi.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he has his own service in this place, where only Hasidim usually go to such a place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My father, though he was clean-shaven but on Shabbat, we-- he wore a silk garment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we also had-- me and my brother, as little boys-- we also had such silk, little kapotes, they were called.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we only wore them when we went to this rabbi because it was the normal garb that one wore when you went to-- to see a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I said before, my father was a businessman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he basically came from Hasidim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he carried-- he carried on the tradition as far as possible.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He wanted to preserve the tradition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's why on Shabbat we used to wear these garments.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But otherwise-- also, the school we went to was very-- it was under the auspices of the Agudat Yisrael, which is a very orthodox organization.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And most of the children in that school, came from very Hasidic families.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I remember when my father used to come to visit-- to see us to speak to the teachers in school, I always felt embarrassed because he didn't have a beard.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I always used to feel ashamed that he didn't have a beard, for the other boys.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They shouldn't tease me.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
